text: The Central Coast Mariners FC–Western Sydney Wanderers FC rivalry is a soccer rivalry in the A-League Men, the A-League Women and the A-League Youth. It is played between Central Coast Mariners FC and Western Sydney Wanderers FC. Category:Soccer rivalries in Australia Category:Central Coast Mariners FC Category:Western Sydney Wanderers FC
title: Central Coast Mariners FC–Western Sydney Wanderers FC rivalry
